subtitleNullable: Dataset for classification. Data is combined from many sources (Kaggle, Google)
descriptionNullable:
in final_train.csv, query is the column to be classified.

p1, p2, p3 in final train csv are passages related to the query sourced from Covid 19 Open Research Dataset. Some of the p1, p2, p3 are also sourced from other datasets.

You can opt out of using p1, p2, p3 or use your own.

The final_train_labels file contain the 0/1 target

Data are sourced from google dataset and kaggle
